---

## Accessibility Checklist
For every asset:
- Add alt text
- Keep contrast high
- Use minimal on-image text
- Caption every Reel and Short
- Keep slides simple and readable
- Use plain language

---

## Product Naming Check
Use these names consistently:
- **WPShadow Core** = free plugin
- **WPShadow Guardian** = local monitoring system inside WPShadow Core
- **WPShadow Cloud** = planned SaaS platform
- **Cloud Guardian diagnostics** = cloud-based diagnostics

Avoid:
- Calling WPShadow Guardian a separate plugin
- Presenting WPShadow Cloud as fully available unless clearly marked as planned

---

## Community Management Checklist
Daily:
- Reply to comments within one business day
- Save audience questions for future content
- Leave 3–5 helpful Reddit comments before posting your own thread
- Avoid leading with product mentions on Reddit

---

